### Step 5: Update end-of-turn-check.sh

Add blocking exit codes:
```bash
# TypeScript errors = BLOCK
if [ $TS_ERRORS -gt 0 ]; then
    echo "❌ BLOCKED: Fix TypeScript errors before ending session"
    exit 1
fi

# Progress file not updated = BLOCK
if [ "$PROGRESS_UPDATED" = "false" ]; then
    echo "❌ BLOCKED: Update claude-progress.txt before ending session"
    exit 1
fi
```

