## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------------|
| False positives block legitimate work | Add `--force` bypass flag |
| Workflow context stale after crash | Auto-expire after 4 hours |
| Too strict blocks productivity | Start with warnings, then blocking |

