## Recommended Approach

**Phase 1 (Today):**
- Strengthen bmad-enforcement.sh with better detection
- Keep as advisory but improve messaging

**Phase 2 (Later):**
- Add workflow context tracking
- Add PreToolUse validation
- Enable blocking mode

This graduated approach prevents workflow disruption while building toward full enforcement.
